@startuml
[*] --> Assigned
Assigned --> [*] : removed from assignment
Assigned --> Unassigned : switch to another assignment
Unassigned --> Assigned : assign to client or campaign
Assigned --> Archived : staff member left job and record archived after some time

state Unemployed {
  [*] --> Unemployed
}

Unemployed --> Assigned : staff member hired again
@enduml
